The second season of Hataraku Maou-sama! MgRonalds best demon lord worker is back, climbing the corporate ladder to become ruler of Earth. But Maous plans of domination might need to be put on hold when a small girl claims to be his and Emis child! (Source: Crunchyroll)
Comedy, Psychological, Romance, Slice of Life, Supernatural

Wracked by insomnia and wanderlust, Kou Yamori is driven onto the moonlit streets every night in an aimless search for something he cant seem to name. His nightly ritual is marked by purposeless introspection until he meets Nazuna, who might just be a vampire! Kous new companion could offer him dark gifts and a vampires immortality. But there are conditions that must be met before Kou can sink his teeth into vampirism, and hell have to discover just how far hes willing to go to satisfy his desires before he can heed the Call of the Night!
(Source: Sentai Filmworks)
Enzai de Shokei Sareta Koushaku Reijou wa Konse de wa Mofu Kami-sama to Odayaka ni Sugoshitai
Fantasy, Romance, Slice of Life, Supernatural

Catriona Julie Grande, the daughter of a marquis, was the Crown Princes fiancee. She was executed under false charges but went back in time. All she wanted was to live her life peacefully and prevent the same tragic fate from occurring again. But one day, the Prince appears in her life again and everything begins to fall apart. She has no idea what to do!
(Source: MangaUpates)
Nae Dongsaeng Geondeulmyeon Neohuineun Da Jugeun Moksumida

One day, I woke up as Rosalite, the older sister of Asterion in the novel, Asterion of the Twilight. I may not be the main character, but its not so bad. Rosalites little brother, though, is fated to die in the story at 20 and that just seems really unfair after all the drama hes been through (did I mention his story is a BL?). Now that Im Rosalite, I decide to save him. But no matter how hard I try, he just keeps dying and every time he dies, I turn back into 16-year-old Rosalite. Ten or so deaths later, Im more determined than ever to save him. Rich, royal, or sexy foreigner: whoever touches my little brother will die!
(Source: Tappytoon)
